        {
            "title": "恒基地產The Henderson於倫敦「國際房地產大獎」榮奪三項殊榮",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15596402&amp;cantoneseUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2026%2F01%2Fbpt2a-15596402-friendly_person-071705.mp3&amp;mandarinUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2026%2F01%2Fbpt2am-15596402-friendly_person-071705.mp3\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒基地產繼上周五(1月16日)宣佈慶祝成立50周年，及其位於中環的超甲級商業項目The Henderson出租率創新高達九成，周二(1月20日)再度傳來好消息。在剛剛於英國倫敦舉行的「國際房地產大獎」（International Property Awards）中，The Henderson成功擊敗全球對手榮獲三項殊榮，包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」、「Best International Commercial High Rise Development（最佳國際商業高層發展）」，以及「Best Commercial High Rise Development Asia Pacific（最佳商業高層發展 - 亞太區）」，再次彰顯集團在全球房地產業界的領先地位及影響力。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/497x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/497x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">The Henderson是「國際房地產大獎」創立至今，唯一一個獲頒發「World’s Best Property」大奬的香港項目，而恒基地產亦是首個本地發展商獲得此殊榮。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/497x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/497x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/960x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/960x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_02.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_02.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_03.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_03.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #54446b\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #54446b\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/497x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">其中包括國際級別大獎「World’s Best Property （世界最佳物業）」。恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/960x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_02.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_03.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">恒基提供圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/960x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/960x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒基提供圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「國際房地產大獎」為全球地產界的重要奬項之一，於1993年創立，旨在表揚全球在建築設計、地產開發、室內設計、行銷等領域有卓越表現的頂尖企業與項目，評選涵蓋設計、品質、服務、創新和永續性等範疇。今屆共有 3,000 個來自全球五個區域，包括歐洲、亞太地區、中東、美洲和非洲的項目爭奪殊榮。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_02.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_02.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒基提供圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"恒基提供圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_03.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"恒基提供圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/528x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_cr_souce-licensed_The-Henderson_03.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">恒基提供圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
