            "title": "全日收市︱連跌4日 恒指跌76點報26487點 「ATMXJ」幾全跌 金融與地產撐市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後反覆再回，於10天線得而復失，落實大市四連跌。重磅科股拖低大市，滙控(00005)則反彈，連同其他金融與地產股撐市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開19點，初段原本反覆偏好，一度衝上26638點，升74點，重越10天線(最新約為26609點)，未幾便掉頭下滑，早市中段最多曾跌200點，低見26363點，其後迅速反彈，將跌幅數窄至不足百點，午後初段再次倒升，但午市中段又一次於10天線得而復失重新轉跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報26487點，跌76點或0.26%；4日累計共回吐512點或1.9%。恒生科技指數全日跑輸大市，收跌66點或1.16%，報5683點；國企指數跌39點或0.43%，報9094點。主板成交略為回升至2377.66億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15597198-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c4%e6%97%a5-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c76%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126487%e9%bb%9e-%e3%80%8catmxj%e3%80%8d%e5%b9%be%e5%85%a8%e8%b7%8c-%e9%87%91",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 16:24:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指跑贏收跌不足1點 深指挫0.97% 芯片股跌勢加劇",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市午後氣氛稍有改善，滬市相對跑贏，幾乎完全收復早市的失地。芯片股跌勢加劇，寒武紀(688256.SH)收挫逾半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寒武紀官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-web_688256-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寒武紀官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早輕微高開2點後，初段曾一鼓作氣衝上4128點，將升幅擴大至14點，但隨即轉勢向下，一度失守4100點，最低曾見4080點，倒跌33點，但於早市中段喘穩，跌幅逐步收窄，午市反覆趨穩；滬指最後收報4113點，跌不足1點或0.01%，成交回升至1.22萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指相對弱勢，初段高位14337點時僅升43點，於開市不足10分鐘已開始轉跌，早市中段最多曾挫260點，低見14033點，有下試萬四點之勢，其後稍為喘定，跌幅亦見收窄，但午後一直跌逾百點；深指收報114155點，跌幅收窄至138點或0.97%，成交略增至1.56萬億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌15點或0.33%，以4718點收市；創業板指數挫59點或1.79%，報3277點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股普遍受壓，寒武紀最低見1331.02元，跌6.24%；收報1343.04元，仍跌5.4%。中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)跌2.48%，報122.18元；華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)也跌1.38%，報133.21元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15596953-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%91%e8%b4%8f%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b31%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab0-97-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e5%8a%a0%e5%8a%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 15:19:01",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
